column2: SELECT ALL   p.objID, p.RA, p.DEC,   p.fiberMag_u, p.fiberMag_g, p.fiberMag_r,   p.petroMag_u, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMag_r,p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMag_i,p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMag_z,p.petroMagErr_z,   s.z, s.zErr,   gal.tauv_cont,   gal_ext.oh_p5#,   gal_ext.lgm_tot_p5#,   gal_ext.sfr_tot_p5#,   p.deVAB_r,   p.expAB_r,   p.modelMag_r,   s.MJD,   s.fiberID,   s.plate into mydb.test_table_bigsample from PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN galSpecIndx AS gal ON gal.specobjid = s.specobjid    JOIN galSpecExtra AS gal_ext ON gal_ext.specobjid = s.specobjid     WHERE     p.petroMag_r <#    AND p.petroMag_g <#   AND p.petroMag_u <#   AND p.fiberMag_r-p.petroMag_r<#   AND s.class=&&&    AND s.z>#   AND s.z<#   AND s.snMedian_u > #   AND s.snMedian_g > #   AND s.snMedian_r > #   AND s.snMedian_i > #   AND s.snMedian_z > #
